Building on the answer by @anon01, this is how to do it in Groovy:

    Map&lt;String,String&gt; getQueryParameters( HttpExchange httpExchange )
	{
		def query = httpExchange.getRequestURI().getQuery()
		return query.split( &#39;&amp;&#39; )
				.collectEntries {
			String[] pair = it.split( &#39;=&#39; )
			if (pair.length &gt; 1)
			{
